column5: Heading up to Miskwabi Lake this long weekend to fish for some lakers.  Wondering how the lakes in the Haliburton area have been doing over the last couple weeks? I will post a report when I get back.  Burt
Spent last saturday ice drinking for lakers on boshkong and caught 2 small ones and one in the slot. Alot of slush on the ice, current areas are not so good, Take care.  FD
